# Known Malicious Domains - APT29
alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"V-Sentinel APT29 Known Malicious Domain"; flow:established,to_server; content:"Host:"; http.header; content:"avsvmcloud.com"; fast_pattern; distance:0; metadata:impact critical, service http; reference:url,attack.mitre.org/groups/G0016/; sid:20260013; rev:1;)

alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"V-Sentinel APT29 Known Malicious Domain"; flow:established,to_server; content:"Host:"; http.header; content:"databasegalore.com"; fast_pattern; distance:0; metadata:impact high, service http; reference:url,attack.mitre.org/groups/G0016/; sid:20260014; rev:1;)

